    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, increase the heat to high and add your <strong>lamb mince</strong></p><p>Cook for 3-4 min further or until browned all over, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p>",
