    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the lamb is browned, add the <strong>chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and <strong>curry powder</strong> and cook for 4 min further or until cooked through and fragrant (no pink meat!)</p>",
