      "instruction": "<p>Once the lamb is done, squeeze in the<strong> </strong>juice<strong> </strong>of 1/4 of the<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lemon[s]</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spiced lamb mince</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
