      "instruction": "<p>Fill the <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>tortillas</strong> with the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>spiced lamb mince</strong> and <strong>tomato salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>coriander chutney</strong> all over and garnish with the <strong>remaining chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
